text:
You may be wondering what the JAY stands for in Henry Jay Eyering. 
It stands for 'just jonking', as in 'I'm just jonking your chain buddy' #jonks
I'm pretty stoked for the Tarkov wipe coming up. It's going to be a good summer boys. #tarkov #escapefromtarkov
The whole deal with Elon and the crypto situation is pretty sad. Things were looking pretty good this summer before he came along
I love Elon and I think he's a genius, but things were better before he got involved.
I'm expecting the market to pick back up maybe late summer early fall. imo the bull market didn't 'end' but it's just going to be a much slower bull market.

maybe an unpopular opinion: Rexburg is a wonderful place.

not just saying that because I've never lived anywhere else, I've just had lots of cool things happen to me here. 
meaningful memories make a place meaningful. #rexburg

One of my favorite #rexburg memories happened late one night while I was riding my bike down the hill by the temple. It was dark and there was no body around. I stood up on the pedals, took both hands off the handlebars, and proceeded to take a whiz all the way down the hill.
Guys, we are getting close to a 50% vaccination rate for the whole US! It won't be long before we put this whole thing behind us. #vaccine
#jonks #bolivia #myjonks my fav food is a cantaloupe and this will never change.
Does jonks sound innapropriate to you guys? as in, She wants me for my jonks. #jonks #bringbackthejonks

Henry means 'house ruler'. 
The name is made up of two parts: "Heim" which means home and "Ric" which means ruler. This is my house and I am the unopposed and absolute ruler. #idaho #rexburg #byui
